window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A devastating attack by the lich&nbsp;Quatach-Ichl has left Zorian and Zach reeling as their remaining restarts tick away.</b></p> <p>As they recover, they make preparations for their final confrontations with Red Robe, the lich, the primordial being, and the invaders—all within the shadow of a question they can’t answer: can Zorian and Zach both survive outside the time loop?</p> <p>When the time loop is broken, sacrifices will be made, bonds will be tested, and trust will be more important than any magical skill or power—and even then, success is not guaranteed.</p> <p>But unbeknownst to his allies, Zorian made another plan in secret…</p>"; 
